{
  "stem": "22944.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was such a-- this is a-- probably the most powerful experience because I was a child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wanted to live.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did not know-- we had to sit there in utter silence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the feeling is that we were told we were caught.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we can hear, actually, the German speaking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We could actually hear the rattling of the key.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We can hear that someone tries to open the, the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, it was so powerful, we just could not understand that the keyhole-- that the key did not open.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that, that we could not understand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We did not know that the key has been switched.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we did not know that Pernik managed to talk him into it, that we came out of his apartment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was so drunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because in the apartment next door, they sat very long time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They must have probably finished a bottle of vodka or Slivovitz, or whatever they were drinking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I think he-- they must have just poured all the time more and more drink into him because that was the only way they could hope that they can confuse him.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Even he believed it was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we all believed it was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was just not any other explanation because they didn't miss any apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the feeling was-- I just remember the whole thing very clearly like today-- the rattling of the key in the keyhole.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
